#  S2S Gateway Web Service

## Description

Provide API for S2S Profile Registration (Client or Admin)

## API

### Client Registration

{

"endpoint": "https://abc.com",
"profileSts": "inactive",
"tswId": "P123456789",
"cert": "",
"traderName": "test",
"contactPerson": "test",
"email": "test@varmeego.com",
"phone": "12345678",
"profileAccountSts": "inactive"
}
